T01TD1164E:237a-1: panytsa ta th'a ga ta sta ba:/
T01TD1164E:237a-3: de bzhin gshegs pa lnga la bstod pa //
T01TD1164E:237a-4: gsung gi mnga' bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1164E:237a-5: 'jig rten gsum mgon yon tan mtha' med pha rol phyin //
T01TD1164E:237a-6: 'o ma'i mtsho ltar dkar yangs mdzes pa'i sku dang ldan //
T01TD1164E:237a-7: mnyam med de bzhin nyid dngos seng ge'i khri la bzhugs //
T01TD1164E:237a-8: thub mchog rnam par snang ba de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1164E:237a-9: mdangs ldan nor bu mthon ka chen po ltar 'phro ba'i //
T01TD1164E:237a-10: 'od kyis phyogs rnams ma lus snang bar mdzad pa po //
T01TD1164E:237a-11: 'jig rten gsum na rmad byung glang po'i khri la bzhugs //
T01TD1164E:237a-12: bsnyengs bral sangs rgyas mi bskyod de la rtag phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1164E:237a-13: rin chen dbang bskur 'byor bas 'gro don mdzad la mkhas //
T01TD1164E:237b-0: @237b bsod nams tshogs mnga' ri rgyal mngon sum rgyu 'dra zhing //
T01TD1164E:237b-1: gser gyi rgya mtsho lta bus rta yi gdan la bzhugs //
T01TD1164E:237b-2: thub pa rin chen 'byung ldan de la rtag phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1164E:237b-3: rma bya'i rigs gsal brgya yis mdzes byas snang ba yi //
T01TD1164E:237b-4: 'od kyis phyogs kun khebs pas mngon dga' pad+ma ni //
T01TD1164E:237b-5: r'a ga'i ri bo ltar mdzes rma bya'i gdan bzhugs pa //
T01TD1164E:237b-6: thub pa dpag med 'od mnga' de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1164E:237b-7: dam chos 'od zer tshogs kyis mun pa sel mdzad pa'i //
T01TD1164E:237b-8: 'od kyi snang bas nam mkha'i cha kun rnam par 'gengs //
T01TD1164E:237b-9: bee d'urya yi mtsho ltar mkha' lding gdan la bzhugs //
T01TD1164E:237b-10: sangs rgyas don yod grub pa de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1164E:237b-11: seng ge glang po rta dang rma bya mkha' lding gdan la rdo rje skyil krung bzhugs //
T01TD1164E:237b-12: sku mdog rim bzhin dkar dang sngo dang ser dang dri med dmar dang ljang gyur cing //
T01TD1164E:237b-13: byang chub mchog dang sa reg mchog sbyin ting 'dzin mi 'jigs sbyin pa'i phyag rgyas mtshan //
T01TD1164E:237b-14: rang rigs rin chen cod pan ldan pa'i ye shes lnga yi bdag nyid de la 'dud //
T01TD1164E:237b-15: de bzhin gshegs pa lnga'i bstod pa rdzogs so /
T01TD1164E:237b-17: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po pad+ma ka ra warma dang /
T01TD1164E:237b-18: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba dge slong rin chen bzang pos bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa//
